<h1 class='text-center mb-4'> HMC Apointment Portal Admin Panel </h1>

<div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="jumbotron app-overlay">
          <h1 class="display-4">APPOINTMENTS</h1>
          <hr class="my-4">
          <p>Appointments are created when users book appointments on the website. Nurses who are administering tests can find the appointment here
          to create a record of the test they administer.</p>
          <%= link_to 'Appointments', appointments_path, class:"btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="jumbotron test-overlay">
        <h1 class="display-4">TESTS</h1>
        <hr class="my-4">
        <p>When a nurse administers a test, they create a record for that test here. When tests are completed and apporved an email of the test 
        cetificate is sent to the person who booked the appointment.</p>
        <%= link_to 'Tests', appointment_tests_path, class:"btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row justify-content-left text-center">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="jumbotron u-overlay">
          <h1 class="display-4">USERS</h1>
          <hr class="my-4">
          <p>Manage different types of users who interface with the HMCAP system.</p>
          <%= link_to 'Users', '#', class:"btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="jumbotron location-overlay">
        <h1 class="display-4">LOCATIONS</h1>
        <hr class="my-4">
        <p>View and edit the locations which are currently on the HMCAP system.</p>
        <%= link_to 'Locations', locations_path, class:"btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="jumbotron chart-overlay">
        <h1 class="display-4">STATISTICS</h1>
        <hr class="my-4">
        <p>View statistics on appointments and tests which are on the HMCAP system.</p>
        <%= link_to 'Statistics', '#', class:"btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
        </div>
    </div>
</div><br/>